author: Mishaal Rahman
title: FlashFire v0.54 Pre-Release Version now Available for Google Pixel and Pixel XL
text: XDA Senior Recognized Developer Chainfire has released a pre-release version of his popular on-device firmware flashing application, FlashFire . This experimental version adds support for the Google Pixel and Pixel XL. Do note that this release is for testing only and contains a few bugs, but once the final version is released â€“ future OTA updates for rooted devices should be effortless.
